White joss paper was used to create this headpiece. I took the beautiful texture of the paper and burned the raw edges and added accents of gold to celebrate the use of this paper.

Thank you @sonder_mpls @iamsarahedwards for having me! It was such a great event to bring the world of art to the community through this immersive experience! I was able to showcase my newest installation, Phase. Hope you enjoy the process of how it all came together ☺️

PHASE // The many phases of life’s journeys can be seen just as light and shadow that make up how we view the world. The shadows casted by the multiple layers fill our network of time, shaped by our ever-changing experiences.

#artist #installationart #handcut #mplsart #sonder #art
